room_title: Escape room "Mystery Lodge" by A-Escape in Asheville
room_address: 353 New Leicester Hwy Asheville, NC, 28806 Office Suite F
room_description: Great Uncle Lou's Mystery Lodge is full of all sorts of wondrous and bizarre collections! UFOs? Bigfoot? Ghosts? You name it! When a greedy businessman hatches a plot to tear down the Mystery Lodge and open a car wash, it's up to you and your friends to solve the riddles within the Lodge and save the day! Work through cryptids, magic DVDs, and mesmerizing puzzles in this fun-filled room!
